IMMEDIATE
No. 55/4/CF-62
GOVERNMEN T OF INDIA
CABINET SECRETARIAT
( Department of Cabinet Affairs)
New Delhi, the 21st November 1962.
seta
The undersigned is directed to state that, with effect
from the forenoon of November 21, 1962, the Prime Minister has
relinquished the office of Minister of Defence; and Shri Y. B.
Chavan has assumed the office of Minister of Defence.
( B. G. Rau )
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
All Members of the Council of Ministers.
Copy forwarded to the Principal Private Secretary to the
Prime Minister/the Private Secretary to the Prime Minister,
information.
P.T.O.

Copy forwarded to the Secretary to the President/the
Private Secretary to the Vice-President, for information.
( B. G. Rau)
Joint Secretary to the Cabinet.
Copy forwarded to all Secretaries/Special S ecretaries/
Additional Secretaries to the Government of India/Chairman.
Railway Board/Secretary, Election Commission, for information.
Copy forwarded to all Ministries of the Goverment of
India/Department of Parliamentary Affairs/Planning Commission/
Department of Atomic Energy/Prime Minister's Secretariat/
Lok Sabha S ecretariat/Rajya Sabha Secretariat, for info mation.
( D. P. Chopra )
Under Secretary to the Cabinet.
